snippet.title: Kana Quest Release Dates
snippet.description:
A Kawaii Kana Match-Em Up is coming soon to Nintendo Switch on March 28th! Learn Japanese. Match Kana (Japanese letters) with their sounds. Solve Puzzles. Your quest to learn Japanese starts now!

Buy Now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/725850/Kana_Quest/

https://twitter.com/KanaQuest

Press & Influencer Inquiries: press@whitehthorngames.com
